Member Function Documentation

XFCIMPORT UINT32 XFcPixelConverter::convert (  UINT32    aSource,
INT32    aSourceFormat,
INT32    aTargetFormat
)  [static]
 

Converts a single pixel between two specified pixel formats.

Parameters:
aSource source pixel.
aSourceFormat source buffer pixel format, see XFCGFXFORMAT.
aTargetFormat target buffer pixel format, see XFCGFXFORMAT.
Returns:
converted pixel in the requested target format.
See also:
XFCGFXFORMAT
Note:
this is not meant to be fast. Please use the XFCPC_ macros from XFcPixelConverter.h to perform fast operations.
